OL,5,Cextended
OL,7,FHowever, there is still no indication
OL,8,Fof how the military experts will
OL,9,Fdispose of the device more than 80
OL,10,Fhours after the major incident was
OL,11,Fdeclared.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for NHS Devon said:
OL,14,F"NHS Devon has declared a critical
OL,15,Fincident status for health in Devon.
OL,17,F"This is a precautionary action so the
OL,18,Fsystem can take the necessary steps in
OL,19,Fresponse to the unexploded bomb in
OL,20,FPlymouth, which has been declared as a
OL,21,Fmajor incident led by the police.
