OL,5,Cextended
OL,7,F"We are in Critical Incident at UHP
OL,8,F(University Hospitals Plymouth) to
OL,9,Fsupport the system response to the
OL,10,Fmajor incident in the city and to
OL,11,Freduce the pressure on our services.
OL,13,F"Declaring an internal critical
OL,14,Fincident allows us to make decisions
OL,15,Fbehind the scenes to improve patient
OL,16,Fflow across the hospital.
OL,18,F"This can include the cancellation and
OL,19,Frescheduling of certain planned
OL,20,Foperations based on clinical need."
