OL,7,FPaul Laity, an inspector at Devon and
OL,8,FCornwall Police, said: "It is their
OL,9,Fchoice. They need to be made aware of
OL,10,Fthe risks of staying and that's
OL,11,Fhappened with door knocks and letter
OL,12,Fdrops, but we cannot force people out
OL,13,Fof their homes.
OL,15,F"But they just need to understand
OL,16,Fthere is risk to life and risk to
OL,17,Fproperty with an incident like this."
